Hi All,

So AWS JAVA SDK does not work with Walrus. This is in continuation to the current on-going work mentioned here https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/browse/EUCA-3001

AWS JAVA SDK was built and used as mentioned in the above JIRA ticket, following code was tested:

{code}
